Late Delivery and Penalty. In case of delayed delivery of Goods, [{seller}] (the Seller) shall pay to [{buyer}] (the Buyer) shall pay a penalty amounting to [{penaltyPercentage}]% of the total value of the Goods for every [{penaltyDuration}] of delay. The total amount of penalty shall not, however, exceed [{capPercentage}]% of the total value of the delayed goods. If the delay is more than [{maximumDelay}], the Buyer is entitled to terminate this Contract.
